ontents and mutability.\n\nUpdated Native Image test metadata:\n- `tests/src/org.scala-lang/scala-library/2.11.8/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/reachability-metadata.json`\n  - Added serialization/reflection metadata for:\n    - `scala.collection.mutable.UnrolledBuffer`\n    - supporting Scala `Int` manifest\n    - the test helper serialization subclass\n\nValidation:\n- Confirmed the metadata JSON parses successfully.\n- Did not compile or run tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ab3df24a8af6ee70169f52909b020819f97282d8829853726\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 935, "output": 1670, "cacheRead": 42496, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 45101, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777674484019, "responseId": "resp_0ab3df24a8af6ee70169f528f49608819fae9a1d11c1708449"}, "toolResults": []}
